es transitively, includes its own Native Image Netty system properties, and the failing coverage is in local value/object-mapping APIs rather than a Neo4j server connection.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"End-to-end Driver/session/query coverage would require a running Neo4j server, but that is not necessary for the current java-run failure or the existing meaningful mapping/value coverage.\",\n    \"Optional integrations such as Micrometer logging/metrics, SLF4J, Bouncy Castle certificate handling, or BlockHound should not be added unless the generated tests intentionally target those optional features.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0d4cbf61e773455c016a422feba61c8194824f706eb4dde5f3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1745, "output": 1035, "cacheRead": 24576, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 27356, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782722526358, "responseId": "resp_0d4cbf61e773455c016a422fded57c8194a7f7322ea34474c7"}}
